A listener that listen to the position (index) of the current showed photo in fullscreen mode, in other words it listen to the scroll of the recycler view, and when the current photo is changed we notify the Main activity that the scroll position is changed, so in her turn can notify other fragments that the scroll position is changed, so they can keep their scrolling synced for the user, when back to the other fragments.
